The AI tool will analyze the posts of LinkedIn Influencers and help them to create the new posts based on the writing style as per the their earlier posts
User is suppose to select the tag/topics, length and langauge for the post.
The projects works as per the below steps
1. Collect LinkedIn posts and generate raw JSON file with post and additional parameters
2. Process the raw JSON analyze using llama 3.2 model and make processed JSON with post with parameters Tags, Langauge and Length
3. Generate prompt with selected inputs from user and filtered posts from processed json based on selected inputs, give those post as an example to prompt to build a post as per the style using Llama 3.2 model.

The pre-requisites for this project is mentioned in requirements.txt file
To get started first install the dependencies 
Run the streamlit app using below command-
streamlit run main.py 
